Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.62,0:10:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,真是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,还是回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.18,0:11:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,说笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.60,0:11:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,蝙蝠人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.54,0:14:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.98,0:14:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,注意点 不会掉下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.09,0:15:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.55,0:15:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,救…救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.14,0:16:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不要掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:16:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,掉下去…是掉到哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.88,0:16:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么问这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.56,0:18:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,和拉格斯的画一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,拉格斯…这不是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你是颠倒人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,什么颠倒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.79,0:18:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,什么啊 这里怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.89,0:18:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这个也是 那个也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.19,0:18:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,全都从上面倒吊着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,倒吊的…是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.63,0:18:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,什么啊 明明是你从上面…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.33,0:18:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,蝙蝠人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 你也是那家伙的同伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙也是颠倒的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.36,0:18:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我会遇到这种不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.92,0:18:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,让我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.92,0:18:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我说了等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.19,0:18:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是我让你遭遇不幸的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.34,0:18:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不会那样做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.73,0:18:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,就因为你是颠倒人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.87,0:19:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.72,0:19:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.71,0:19:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你被谁袭击了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.25,0:19:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.04,0:19:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了 我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.35,0:19:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.81,0:19:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,给我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.19,0:19:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.77,0:19:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,要把我一个人留在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,可是要是不去学校的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.23,0:19:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,市民资格…监视什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.71,0:19:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我和学校哪个比较重要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.50,0:19:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的 我会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.76,0:20:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,说好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.29,0:20:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.34,0:20:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以把我一个人留在这里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.55,0:20:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.16,0:20:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,要对蝙蝠人要保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.89,0:20:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.40,0:20:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.97,0:20:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.25,0:20:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你还真是公主范
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.07,0:20:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你不要说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.18,0:20:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫艾吉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么称呼你好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.36,0:20:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫帕特玛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.33,0:21:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,飞了
